passages.text:
''Finished!''
''Try to stand up, love.''

//[[I don't want to.|MD2.1]]
[[I don't feel well enough.|MD4]]//
[[Stand up.|MD3]]
//[[Grrrr.|MD2.2]]//

''Really?''
''Come on. I will catch you if you fall.''

//[[Always?|MD4.1]]
[[I can't.|MD4.2]]//
[[You stand up.|MD3]]
//[[I don't trust you.|MD4.2]]//

''Right.''
''What day is it?''

//[[August 26th.|LM2]]//

''This is completely normal, sweetheart. Don't worry. It will be fine, Kim is a good friend of me.''
<<if visited ("LM3.3")>>''Since you are moving in with him, you should be scared. It's a big step forward, but I believe you'll love it.''<</if>>

//[[Yes? ... I am relieved. I trust you.|LM7]]//

''Don't be.''
''I will always be there for you, love. I was made for you. There is no bond stronger than between the mother and the child.''

//[[I am not a program.|Mother3.2]]//
//[[You are not my mother. You are a program.|Mother14]]//
<<if visited ("MOTHER4") > 0>>[[Again you stay silent, trying hard to wake up.|MOTHER4]] <<else>>[[You stay silent, trying to wake up.|MOTHER4]]<</if>>

<<set $mother3 to true>>

''Darkness is nothing to fear. Try to relax and concentrate on my voice. It will be fine.''

//[[Okay.|MA2.3]]//

<<set $fear +=1>>

''Everything all right?''

//[[GnnnNN.|MD4.2]]//

<<set $insanity +=1>>

''There is no reason why you shouldn't.''

//[[Okay.|Mother3.3]]
<<if $mother32 is false>>[[Fuck you.|Mother3.2]]//<<else>>[[Fuck you.|Mother3.3]]<</if>>

''There is no more information on this subject. Choose another one.''

//[[I feel dizzy.|Mother11]]
[[Okay.|Mother3.3]]//
